title: Real Sociedad 0 Barcelona 1: Neymar penalty gives Nou Camp side advantage going into Cope del Rey quarter-final second leg
text:
EFL Ney bother Real Sociedad 0 Barcelona 1: Neymar penalty gives Nou Camp side advantage going into Cope del Rey quarter-final second leg 
Brazilian scored from the spot but was later booked for diving while home side did not record a single shot on target all game By Sam Morgan
